%h1.page_heading.center= @gCheckoutInProgress ? 'Billing Information' : 'Create Your Account'

#inner_wrapper
  %p 
    Questions about this page? Already have an account but forgot your password?
    = link_to_function 'Click here.', visual_effect(:toggle_slide,'FAQ')
  %fieldset#FAQ{:style => 'display: none'}
    %legend FAQs
    %dl
      %dt Why do you need my email address?
      %dd To communicate with you about your order in case there is a problem.
      %dt Why do you need my name and billing address?
      %dd 
        For credit card ticket purchase.  
        %strong= link_to( "We never share  this information with anyone and we do not store credit card information.",Option.value(:privacy_policy_url))
        Choosing a password protects access to your account. 
      %dt I'm a Subscriber, but I couldn't retrieve my password.
      %dd 
        All Subscribers already have accounts containing your subscription
        information and vouchers.  Go to the 
        = link_to 'Login screen', :controller =>  'customers', :action => 'login'
        and check the "Forgot Password" box. If you need further help, email
        = mail_to(Option.value(:help_email),nil,:encode=>"hex", :subject=>"Help with Audience1st account for #{Option.value(:venue)}")
        with your full name and billing address and we'll be happy to help.
      %dt Under 18?  
      %dd
        Patrons under 18 are required to get the
        permission of a parent or adult guardian before providing any contact
        information on this site.
      %dt Under 13? 
      %dd
        Sorry, but in accordance with 
        = link_to "COPPA", "http://www.ftc.gov/ogc/coppa1.htm"
        you may not use this site. 

  - if @is_admin
    - form_tag :action => 'create' do
      = render :partial => 'password' 
      = render :partial => 'form'
      = render :partial => 'form_admin'
      = submit_tag "Create New User Account"
      = gen_button 'Cancel', :action => :list
  - else
    - form_tag :action => 'user_create' do
      = render :partial => 'form'
      = render :partial => 'password'
      = submit_tag (@gCheckoutInProgress ? 'CONTINUE >>' : 'Create My Account')
      = gen_button 'Cancel', :action => 'login'

